{"tid":1933532,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"今次到德國：萊比錫爆發高致病性H5N8禽流感","createTime":"2020-03-19T10:38:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T11:28:38.000Z","uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b3ffc05e6be66b2571ab2aaa406034dc2ad70bb8","tid":1933532,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T10:38:31.000Z","msg":"本港暫停進口德國薩克森州禽肉及禽類產品<br />\n<br />\n食物安全中心宣布，因德國薩克森州Leipzig區爆發高致病性H5N8禽流感，已即時指示業界，暫停從該地區進口禽肉及禽類產品，包括禽蛋。中心表示，已就事件聯絡德國當局，並會繼續密切留意世界動物衛生組織發出關於爆發禽流感的消息。根據政府統計處的資料，去年本港從德國進口約4780公噸冷藏禽肉及約290萬隻禽蛋。<br />\n<br />\n2020-03-19 18:31:03"},{"pid":"cc942b04266f25b6727dccb6c2086796d6eec8ca","tid":1933532,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T10:40:30.000Z","msg":"德國大肉腸無一個係無辜的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dd8512048cfb0d8392f19759a6626491dc3a4cb","tid":1933532,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T11:28:38.000Z","msg":"DHL 大 hub <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}